WEBVTT

00:01:29.760 --> 00:01:31.640
(Laughter)

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:34.840
I often forget that I'm a little person.

00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:39.320
It's the physical environment
and society that remind me.

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:44.080
Using a public bathroom
is an excruciating experience.

00:01:44.880 --> 00:01:47.056
I walk into the cubicle

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:48.938
but I can't reach the lock on the door.

00:01:49.880 --> 00:01:52.240
I'm creative and resilient.

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:56.400
I look around and see if there's
a bin that I can turn upside down.

00:01:57.400 --> 00:01:58.600
Is it safe?

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:00.240
Not really.